challenge.description: Your team must do the following (and record it): 75 crunches in one sitting, 25 burpees in one set, 10 burpee-suicides in no more than two sets, 15 High Box Jumps in no more than 3 sets, and 15 jumping jacks in one set
Your team must do the following (and record it): 40 Ski Jumps in one set, 3 minutes straight of wall sits, 35 burpees in one set, 25 pull ups each, and run 1 mile with no breaks
